{"tid":2062569,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果今日有列寧雕像被推倒，同破壞歷史名人雕像可唔可以相提並論?","createTime":"2020-06-13T08:31:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T10:32:52.000Z","uid":117332,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a3c7644c608bcc4af1f77b15250e8c3342a9f027","tid":2062569,"uid":117332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T08:31:03.000Z","msg":"列寧雕像比人打爛推例唔知幾多次，但到今日都仲有好多列寧雕像停係到<br />\n<br />\n如果有人反共去打爛佢地，同啲人打破壞哥倫布 南軍將軍 個啲雕像係咪一樣不能容許"},{"pid":"5d1c2a525df5831357adadaef0156526a6554467","tid":2062569,"uid":138409,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T08:34:07.000Z","msg":"呢啲雕像本身就係政治宣傳歌功頌德<br />\n打爛佢根本無所謂<br />\n<br />\n反正睇雕像係學唔到歷史<br />\n要認真學就睇書啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n遠嘅唔講<br />\n台灣一樣有拆除蔣介石銅像嘅訴求<br />\n學術界有所謂「壓迫性事物」嘅講法<br />\n<a href=\"https://opinion.udn.com/opinion/story/6685/3665461\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fopinion.udn.com%2Fopinion%2Fstory%2F6685%2F3665461&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrpFDRn80AWZfiUxX1c6OkmY%3D&h=bc57b073\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://opinion.udn.com/opinion/story/6685/3665461</a><br />\n<br />\n同埋好似Robert E Lee嗰啲銅像<br />\n根本係對黑人民權運動嘅反動<br />\n本身就無歷史價值<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GohlQuOJLpE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGohlQuOJLpE&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrpFDRn80AWZfiUxX1c6OkmY%3D&h=a27d1156\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GohlQuOJLpE</a>"},{"pid":"6f3cc6000ef93d86a4d97430f8d989cbb7fe406a","tid":2062569,"uid":138409,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T08:36:27.000Z","msg":"啲雕像通常係無context<br />\n除左棟響度迫你用仰望角度睇佢之外<br />\n對其他人而言就無其他明顯作用<br />\n<br />\n亦都係點解所謂「拆除銅像 = 破壞歷史」<br />\n係好on9<br />\n<br />\n你睇書獲得嘅歷史知識係有context<br />\n而銅像係連知識都稱唔上"},{"pid":"3cda375868df4a0b4231d5d3f2f5f412948788e8","tid":2062569,"uid":117332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score